    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Screens, partitions, or railings serving to enclose or shut off a space in a building, particularly such structures located in a church, where they are designed to exclude nonworshippers from a chapel or shrine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
